original_title: Disney Princess Sing Along Songs, Vol. 2 - Enchanted Tea Party
overview: It's an enchanted royal tea party, and your little princess is the guest of honor! There, she can sing along with all her favorite Disney Princesses as they perform their best-loved songs. Plus, she'll be the belle of the ball as she learns wonderful dance moves and sings karaoke-style too!
title: Disney Princess Sing Along Songs, Vol. 2 - Enchanted Tea Party
